{"tid":2475578,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–談生酮飲食作癌症輔助治療的可行性","createTime":"2021-04-04T21:56:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T02:55:49.000Z","uid":38861,"like":55,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"fbeb565ca0ae2d1dc873173241ed772f4867cdec","tid":2475578,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T21:56:41.000Z","msg":"癌細胞跟正常細胞一樣，就算處於停止生長的狀態，均需攝取營養維持細胞運作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWYkeiVEN5KPn21houEHsfzoGjg3L1Qz6phmZiLUsW8sP?filename=xC8pOeS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxC8pOeS.jpg&h=c2249a24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在這個基礎下，有不少主張提倡以生酮飲食(Ketogenic Diet)作為醫治癌症的輔助療法。<br />\n究竟這是「武肺乃由5G網路而起」之流，還是有其實質科學實據支持呢?<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）有不少的癌細胞均出現與PI3K蛋白質有關的變異，促使到它們具備更強大的快速繁殖及抵禦進行自我滅亡機制特性。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmcsKMMpYt5JQXkQKqm1tw1pxu2RKtqPkDQLi7GX4U7sQb?filename=9kqLxGz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9kqLxGz.jpg&h=b8440a98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有見及此，科學家們攜手合作，研發出藥物針對已變異的PI3K蛋白質，並在2010年其間進行大量的人類臨床研究，對相應的癌症病人下藥。<br />\n<br />\n遺憾的是，結果非常參差，整體成效並不理想。<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）深入探討為何會失敗後，科學家發現藥物對人體產生了一道副作用，就是誘使肝臟產生糖份，使血糖上升。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZE13zNLwtMmhEHYE2rch6vgyMfSJGo2DVPVKkTUTJvfq?filename=T0V0mzY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT0V0mzY.jpg&h=9cb187e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n胰臟因著血糖的上升而產生胰島素，而非常諷刺的是，胰島素是激勵PI3K蛋白質的物質。<br />\n<br />\n亦即是說，藥物副作用所產生的胰島素，抵消了藥物本來抑制PI3K的功用。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）基於生酮飲食能夠消耗肝臟的糖原，以及維持血液低胰島素水平，科學家嘗試利用生酮飲食來制衡藥物的副作用，並在老鼠模型上取得非常可觀的成果。<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmYuSQpapTjRiqqSxMVUocAS4E7hDCeaoumfEAVZ1hwBL5?filename=ZGJxcGG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGJxcGG.jpg&h=5db2c443&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n現在即將進行子宮內壁膜癌症患者的臨床測試，以生酮飲食再配上PI3K藥物，希望能夠取得理想的成果。<br />\n<br />\n但有一點要注意的是，在某類型血癌及腦癌個案，生酮飲食反之然會鼓吹癌細胞加速生長，這很有可能是因為是某類別的癌細胞特別傾向吸收脂肪或酮體。<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，在尚未摸透自身所患的癌細胞其新陳代謝特性之前，胡亂採取生酮飲食將有機會引來反效果，間接為癌細胞提供有利生長的環境。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RQVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=1ff6480b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RQVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=5bf20972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-018-0343-4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-018-0343-4&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RQVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=6834e408\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-018-0343-4</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/372/6537/20\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2F372%2F6537%2F20&d=pELvyPwarRQ4piNq9SB1RQVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=8a719f33\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/372/6537/20</a>"},{"pid":"02740c9ac697c8761741969f353a7257f6240239","tid":2475578,"uid":83118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T22:07:00.000Z","msg":"強帖留名"},{"pid":"9450288b2c5cec36731a47229ba74683cec952e6","tid":2475578,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T22:33:03.000Z","msg":"薯仔本行<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e179a7833ea917204e3ed9900ae794a614bc88b","tid":2475578,"uid":54323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T22:58:26.000Z","msg":"行李撞擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c9a4f4d9deb265a9cf3c5101174ad4c18a80aac","tid":2475578,"uid":263025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T23:08:17.000Z","msg":"行李撞擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條條大路通羅馬，你係一隻河馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。條大路，條街度，你就得撚咗係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />條大路有更多空間<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/annoyed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你係要得喺中間<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ff21a5b78b34ec8273d8c06e8384f182216dc1","tid":2475578,"uid":16137,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T23:13:28.000Z","msg":"真係醫到癌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n巴打下次可唔可以講下斷食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nd 人吹到斷食可以迫使身體分解老化咗嘅舊細胞達到延年益壽嘅目的，又會刺激生長素分泌，唔知幾成真 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3785c26e1d24e73dbbb2b4fd951f5afc057b095c","tid":2475578,"uid":253004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-04T23:43:38.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"3ef9b40576b645f5da1cfed989f73a881b951b06","tid":2475578,"uid":280648,"like